{"tid":1816472,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不肖人士販賣 TWICE 航程資訊　JYP Entertainment 將採取法律手段追究","createTime":"2020-01-08T09:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T11:40:03.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9caf09e54c87e05de18f4e780db5f867d5b86ad0","tid":1816472,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:11:38.000Z","msg":"最近頻頻傳出威脅 TWICE 人身安全的事件，今日 JYP 也針對不肖人士販賣 TWICE 航程資訊的違法行徑再度發出聲明！<br />\n<br />\nJYP Entertainment 今天（8 日）在 TWICE 的官方網站上發出聲明，表示正在針對流出、販賣藝人航程資訊給予他人的行為尋找能根絕的措施。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJYP 表示已透過若干管道追查販售這類資訊的人，並指出這類行徑觸犯個資保護法，可處 5000 萬韓元以下的罰金或 5 年以下的徒刑，再加上擅自散佈這類資訊同樣犯法，還可能加處 3000 萬韓元以下罰金或 3 年以下徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n在說明行為嚴重性之外，JYP 也表示：「謹向反覆在機場引發安全問題的部份人士再次說明正確的機場秩序，機場不只有藝人會用，也是許多人都會使用的空間，請務必遵守秩序，勿造成困擾。」並強調：「目前已就違反這類秩序者討論法律處理辦法。」無論如何，希望 TWICE 能有更安全的工作和日常環境啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/123327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F123327&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6Iivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=a0eccef0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/123327</a>"},{"pid":"abaeef3df5e609255bf39431900d18d3832fa829","tid":1816472,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/bc27351183c49035c983013429e46c50/a8d6ac1946da83dc-f9/s400x600/5fcda70e5daee63013383da3cdd37b720a736f7a.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fbc27351183c49035c983013429e46c50%2Fa8d6ac1946da83dc-f9%2Fs400x600%2F5fcda70e5daee63013383da3cdd37b720a736f7a.gifv&h=5e64811f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/63d6e331fd63c2fc18610312042589a3/a8d6ac1946da83dc-19/s400x600/4ef9e11667a46c510fe35f3717d484f7788a66d6.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F63